  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK890">
<l>uṭampā ṭilātavar vāḻkkai kuṭaṅkaruḷ</l>
<l>pāmpō ṭuṭaṉuṟain taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Living with those who do not agree (with one) is like dwelling with a cobra (in the same) hut.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
